{"tid":930951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國研究「預防犯罪」系統 未犯事先定罪？","createTime":"2018-12-06T16:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T01:40:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f4dfa35d69796b941aebed56d90d25cec61682b3","tid":930951,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181206/large/1544084030_b55f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181206%2Flarge%2F1544084030_b55f.jpg&h=15a7c2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n罪案無日無之，要如何有效防止罪案發生是世界各地警方的重要議題，但如果可以在罪案發生前未卜先知早一步阻止，創造零犯罪社會，這不是人人期望的烏托邦？<br />\n<br />\n大數據、人工智能這些科技概念，被引入防止罪案調查已是大勢所趨。英國伯明翰所屬的西密德蘭郡警方日前公佈正研發一套名為「國家數據分析方案」（National Data Analytics Solution,NDAS）的電腦系統，預計明年3月推出試驗版，並計劃拓展至全英國警方使用；該系統結合警方數據資料加以分析，聲稱可以預測一個人的犯罪率或無辜受害的機率，讓警方可以提前作出行動。<br />\n<br />\n系統收集的數據，除了個人資料外，當然還有過去的犯罪紀錄、精神病紀錄等等，結合警方身上的監控鏡頭、各地的CCTV、汽車行車紀錄儀，還有社交媒體狀況、留言等，決定每一個人的「犯罪指數」，若系統發現其作出可能對社會構成威脅的行為便會作出警告。<br />\n<br />\n例如：一名有多次傷人案底的積犯被發現出入幫會集結地、之後被追蹤到購入刀具等武器、到陌生的地方等候，警方根據電腦指示認為他有高確率作出傷人犯罪行為，於是率先出動接觸事主；代表NDAS的警方發言人Iain Donnelly表示，警方絕不會「未犯先判」根據NDAS的預測拘捕任何人，只會對有犯罪傾向的人士作出搜查或輔導等協助。<br />\n<br />\n英國學術界對NDAS的實用性仍然存疑，因為系統主要根據巿民的過去紀錄進行預測，對未犯過罪的一般巿民單憑其行為是否能做出預測仍有懷疑，系統更有可能帶出另一個深層次問題；美國警方早已引入另一相似的防止犯罪電腦系統「PREDPOL」，不過PREDPOL並非針對個別人士的犯罪意圖，而是某地區發生罪案的可能性，但有評論指PREDPOL因同樣以個別人士的犯罪紀錄作為依據，令警方對某些低下層地區心存偏見，過份的巡查、搜查反而引起巿民不滿，甚至令原本洗心革面的人士因受到歧視最後再犯案收場。<br />\n<br />\n新科技協助警方預防罪案發生<br />\n<br />\n預測犯罪在執行或道德層面上仍存着很大爭議，而當極權國家掌握並全面實行此等技術，後果可想而知；其實不用想，大陸已經在做了。"},{"pid":"e67b9694c5a6cbe35a4ef5ca522b02b12cb55e24","tid":930951,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又未來報告"},{"pid":"917ff99cb8105c44ee643c7f981ebc2ba10cce7c","tid":930951,"uid":99209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:32:40.000Z","msg":"未來報告"},{"pid":"3e30d057b6aee973095e02ad0240cf0e7c4c2abd","tid":930951,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.globalresearch.ca/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/precrime.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalresearch.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F11%2Fprecrime.jpg&h=61d8d9f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"24d928a601f78870075f800763c8350f1a983d29","tid":930951,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e7225ba2c325665f94e1a28dccb1a4bc48eb2ec","tid":930951,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61846441f7f57b05b11f1266366c4a8ae5236dbd","tid":930951,"uid":116406,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"Psycho-pass"},{"pid":"b0bf71b1a2b818b1f2dc5e85c1022384875528e0","tid":930951,"uid":107297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"Sibyl System"},{"pid":"5bceaccc4ec25f847164ad24b14436fd717bd13d","tid":930951,"uid":17866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:04:16.000Z","msg":"Muslim 拉撚曬佢地去堆田堆海<br />\n之後cancel條法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f74b2621abf6045ffbb2cf182192a8f012a72e","tid":930951,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bceaccc4ec25f847164ad24b14436fd717bd13d","tid":930951,"uid":17866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:04:16.000Z","msg":"Muslim 拉撚曬佢地去堆田堆海<br />\n之後cancel條法例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:07:23.000Z","msg":"仲有堆力架"},{"pid":"5a4c06c4458cfd6664e8330103a09898b69496b6","tid":930951,"uid":43009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:07:57.000Z","msg":"英國研究"},{"pid":"5c1376e48bb485074efd166d7dd2c6c51bbbbcf6","tid":930951,"uid":202051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但有評論指PREDPOL因同樣以個別人士的犯罪紀錄作為依據，令警方對某些低下層地區心存偏見，過份的巡查、搜查反而引起巿民不滿，甚至令原本洗心革面的人士因受到歧視最後再犯案收場。</blockquote><br />\n根本明眼人都知呢種事發生機會微乎其微<br />\n係垃圾區出身嘅罪犯坐完出黎又入番去坐嘅機率高好多<br />\n犯罪率係高尚區定垃圾區高啲更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食屎啦"},{"pid":"af58bc5d0b259c8e7bb6906f1a114696539357b1","tid":930951,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"內農"},{"pid":"7d4c2786c42701571f8b6c46f506b6a82f7e0496","tid":930951,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:18:28.000Z","msg":"未來報告成真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fbf7331769390f61e8ff15bdbea1cb3fe2406d","tid":930951,"uid":224882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61846441f7f57b05b11f1266366c4a8ae5236dbd","tid":930951,"uid":116406,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"Psycho-pass"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:19:22.000Z","msg":"免罪體質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31547a5c8f6a74f4e6985d1c23f1e98a3eaf5ba","tid":930951,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:21:18.000Z","msg":"毒撚末日"},{"pid":"004aa002da366922099309d121d523cf51c123f9","tid":930951,"uid":4420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T01:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxzJ4Xd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxzJ4Xd.jpg&h=a7b28909&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cf3b486ec44c8a9420ee5e9231245c46f891493","tid":930951,"uid":11719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"004aa002da366922099309d121d523cf51c123f9","tid":930951,"u